==Premieres==
The films of the Film Jam 2025 winners were screened by VRChat on [https://twitch.tv/vrchat Twitch].  the winners, along with the honorable mentions, were screened in VRChat by the {{Group link|grp_93f6413e-cd62-4c2d-8d2a-62f4adb15b66|Filmmakers of VRChat}} group.

The premieres were screened at the following times:
* Winners-only: September 20th at 1pm PT
* Second: September 20th at 4pm PT
* Third: September 21st at 3am PT

